"{\"uid\": \"si.com-onsi-athlete-lifestyle-news-revolutionary-war-lebron-james-wins-2024-olympics-opening-ceremony-photos\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"So we might have said the Parade of Nations during the 2024 Olympics Opening Ceremony was a bit... boring.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The photos, on the other hand, were epic.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RELATED:Beheaded Marie Antoinette tops weirdest Olympics Opening Ceremony moments  Flag-bearer LeBron James (along with Coco Gauff)channeled his inner Founding Father when he held the flag for Team USA.\\u00c2  LeBron leading his army to battle (2024)pic.twitter.com/pCjooTca2M  Substitute the driving rain of LeBron holding the flag on the Seine in Paris for George Washington in the freezing-cold ice crossing the Delaware River into Pennsylvania in 1776, and the photo is pricelessly similar.\\u00c2  The original \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWashington Crossing the Delaware\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d was an 1851 painting by artist Emanuel Leutze that is a mainstay in history text books across the country.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 167, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.941213082953462e-24, \"text\": \"Marie Antoinette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}, {\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 270, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"